/// The central processor ingest package namespace.
namespace askap::cp::ingest {};

/// @mainpage ASKAP Central Processor Ingest Pipeline
///
/// @section cpingest_intro Introduction
/// The Central Processor Ingest Pipeline is responsible for the following:
///
/// @li Ingesting visibilities from the correlator
/// @li Ingesting metadata from the telescope operating system
/// @li Annotating visibility stream with metadata
/// @li Calculating uvw coordinates
/// @li Flagging suspect data (e.g. RFI impacted data)
/// @li Applying calibration to the observed visibilities
/// @li Averaging (optional)
/// @li Writing out of measurement set or similar
///
/// @note This package does not provide an externally consumable library & API.
/// This package provides a set of programs.
